items.title: Collection name
items.subtitle: NFT name Ex Shiba Astronaut
items.text: This 3-week English immersion program focuses on developing language skills using Canadian academic content and the UN's Sustainable Development Goals. It emphasizes the knowledge, skills and strategies needed for academic success and is offered twice each year in early spring and summer.
